title: #92Noon at #KFANCombine: Florio/Zimmer/Schefter/Shurmur/Wobby
description: PA, Charch and Nordo are in Indianapolis for the 2018 NFL Combine! PFT's Mike Florio kicks off the show before Vikings Head Coach Mike Zimmer joins the broadcast. NFL Insider Adam Shefter stops by. New Giants Head Coach Pat Shurmur talks to PA about the transition to his new gig from his old gig as Vikings offensive coordinator. And Wobby closes the show talking all things purple, including the Vikings QB situation.
